title: ArkansasVarsity.com Week Six Weekly Blitz
text:
ArkansasVarsity.com Week Six Weekly Blitz Luke Matheson CLICK HERE TO SUBSCRIBE TO ARKANSASVARSITY.COM 
We are now in week six of the 2015 Arkansas high school football season, and there are several great games taking place this week. 
ArkansasVarsity.com publisher Luke Matheson and Gray's Power Poll publisher Steve Gray take a look at several top games this week, including Alma vs. Bryant, Arkadelphia vs. Fountain Lake, Bentonville vs Har-Ber, Conway vs. Greenwood, Harrison vs. Morrilton, Hector vs. Mountainburg, Hope vs. Watson Chapel, Little Rock Christian vs. Vilonia, and North Little Rock vs. Jonesboro. 
Additionally, Steve Gray discusses the Gray's Power Poll system, how it works, how often the poll and predictions are successful, and more. 
You can listen to this week's podcast in the audio player below.
